title: TV Aerial Cable 1m – Male to Male Coaxial Wire with Gold Plated Plugs| Plug-to-Plug Shielded Connectors | Antenna AV Lead for Digital and Analogue Signal Transmission
features: [QUALITY SIGNAL TRANSMISSION using CABLE MOUNTAIN] High Clarity Gold Plated TV Coaxial Cable with fully shield OFC copper pins to minimise interference and maintain high quality signal transfer. This Coax cable is a league above the standard cables supplied with most A/V equipment.

[COMPATIBILITY] Male to Male aerial cable is ideal for connection to wall auxiliary socket, FreeView, Sky Q, YouView, Virgin and other cable/ satellite tv boxes. It is the best choice for connecting your external aerial to your tv to a female wall socket. Male to Female option is available depending on the connection you require.

[HIGH SPEED WITH NO INTERFERENCE] This Rust resistant tv ariel cable offers clear transmission of high-speed Digital and Analogue signals. This tv coaxial cable is Protected with PVC shielding minimizing interference so the signal within the wire are not affected by any other passing wire.

[DURABLE AND LONG LASTING] The Tv cable is durable, flexible and manufactured using the highest quality materials. It provides first-rate Digital reception. It has gold plated ends and a thick copper pin. It has metal die cut plugs with integrated grips to allow for a smooth secure connection.
[BUY WITH CONFIDENCE] We offer a 12 month warranty on all our cables and if you're not completely satisfied with our tv antenna cable. Please contact us for replacement or refund.
